{"tid":343284,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[詞撚]毛不易--消愁 歌詞研究","createTime":"2017-08-01T10:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T02:07:12.000Z","uid":102355,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5628d4ac9b79599523353bca14efff73f2d105f2","tid":343284,"uid":102355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:18:33.000Z","msg":"小弟一直有留意開毛不易寫既詞<br />\n&lt;&lt;如果有一天我變得很有錢&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n&lt;iframe width=&quot;640&quot; height=&quot;360&quot; src=&quot;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Z2R1xEnuxCY&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FZ2R1xEnuxCY%22&d=zyqxBc1rL4iI1hgoV0o7wghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=97330dd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/embed/Z2R1xEnuxCY&quot;</a> frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;<br />\n<br />\n及後既 &lt;&lt;感覺自己是巨星&gt;&gt;<br />\n&lt;iframe width=&quot;640&quot; height=&quot;360&quot; src=&quot;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xnpDRuU0Onk&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FxnpDRuU0Onk%22&d=zyqxBc1rL4iI1hgoV0o7wghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=3e872e0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/embed/xnpDRuU0Onk&quot;</a> frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;<br />\n<br />\n兩首都係走輕鬆路線 到最後帶出道理既詞風<br />\n但最近就再唱咗一首完全唔同曲風既 &lt;&lt;消愁&gt;&gt;<br />\n&lt;iframe width=&quot;640&quot; height=&quot;360&quot; src=&quot;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZHGN3ViWrns&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FZHGN3ViWrns%22&d=zyqxBc1rL4iI1hgoV0o7wghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7690f36d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZHGN3ViWrns&quot;</a> frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;<br />\n<br />\n對於佢既詞基本上係小弟見過寫得最靚既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但對於最後四句 <br />\n<br />\n<em>好吧天亮之後總是潦草離場<br />\n清醒的人最荒唐<br />\n<br />\n好吧天亮之後總是潦草離場<br />\n清醒的人最荒唐﻿</em><br />\n<br />\n利用重複手法帶出重點 反而令我覺得低手咗<br />\n以佢寫嘅詞既水平 我覺得冇必要透過重複去強調<br />\n咁寫好似係刻意降格俾返大眾去聽明 去遷就返普及音樂文化<br />\n以純藝術角度去睇 最後兩句配以另類既詞會否更為有力呢?<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才 試配以兩句<br />\n歡樂場只剩下潦潦數個醉漢<br />\n消愁的人沒失望<br />\n<br />\n又不知效果如何?"},{"pid":"fdfbb0bfc1137fd228ba095d42a46dad55f07c07","tid":343284,"uid":102355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:19:17.000Z","msg":"原詞:<br />\n&lt;消愁&gt;毛不易<br />\n詞/曲：毛不易<br />\n<br />\n當你走進這歡樂場<br />\n背上所有的夢與想<br />\n各色的臉上各色的妝<br />\n沒人記得你的模樣<br />\n三巡酒過你在角落<br />\n固執的唱著苦澀的歌<br />\n聽他在喧囂裡被淹沒<br />\n你拿起酒杯對自己說<br />\n<br />\n一杯敬朝陽一杯敬月光<br />\n喚醒我的嚮往 溫柔了寒窗<br />\n於是可以不回頭地逆風飛翔<br />\n不怕心頭有雨 眼底有霜<br />\n<br />\n一杯敬故鄉 一杯敬遠方<br />\n守著我的善良 催著我成長<br />\n所以南北的路從此不再漫長<br />\n靈魂不再無處安放<br />\n<br />\n一杯敬明天 一杯敬過往<br />\n支撐我的身體 厚重了肩膀<br />\n雖然從不相信所謂山高水長<br />\n人生苦短何必念念不忘<br />\n<br />\n一杯敬自由 一杯敬死亡<br />\n寬恕我的平凡驅散了迷惘<br />\n好吧天亮之後總是潦草離場<br />\n清醒的人最荒唐<br />\n<br />\n好吧天亮之後總是潦草離場<br />\n清醒的人最荒唐﻿"},{"pid":"f637ab90136bbfbceca4ff9af5c9f14f4f71c9d7","tid":343284,"uid":24235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:21:14.000Z","msg":"你係咪第一次開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718ea3763ba78762d5caa7fea6a7f6d89d642398","tid":343284,"uid":10487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:31:39.000Z","msg":"推下起.. 聽左幾十次 消愁 好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2bce8444ffcc077a9e35d28f15dfe831a3733b","tid":343284,"uid":102355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推下起.. 聽左幾十次 消愁 好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同道中人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a466d7167c045839cd4513f59557f8a341c92df","tid":343284,"uid":75116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"我都有聽，幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae52e82d0bb096dab3a17ee79a212b655d008713","tid":343284,"uid":102355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都有聽，幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a93013302d00eb4cde283403af3b5143471d2a5","tid":343284,"uid":3095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:57:49.000Z","msg":"啱啱loop左幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea97788b7f55e8a44c3bc7cad19bd02509cfb70","tid":343284,"uid":98325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<em>好吧天亮之後總是潦草離場<br />\n清醒的人最荒唐<br />\n<br />\n好吧天亮之後總是潦草離場<br />\n清醒的人最荒唐﻿</em><br />\n<br />\n利用重複手法帶出重點 反而令我覺得低手咗<br />\n以佢寫嘅詞既水平 我覺得冇必要透過重複去強調<br />\n咁寫好似係刻意降格俾返大眾去聽明 去遷就返普及音樂文化<br />\n以純藝術角度去睇 最後兩句配以另類既詞會否更為有力呢?<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才 試配以兩句<br />\n歡樂場只剩下潦潦數個醉漢<br />\n消愁的人沒失望<br />\n<br />\n又不知效果如何?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基本上我呢排淨係loop佢首消愁同像我這樣的人。<br />\n<br />\n我自己對於詞方便冇咩研究，不過覺得如果改左做&quot;歡樂場只剩下潦潦數個醉漢<br />\n消愁的人沒失望&quot; 個感覺好似唔太夾。成首歌我理解做主角自己飲酒，敬完朝陽月光....自由死亡舒發完感受之後，&quot;好吧天亮之後總是潦草離場,清醒的人最荒唐&quot; 一句一方便將個故事廷續到第二乾，一方便帶出自己既感受&quot;係呢個歡樂場裡，所有人都係唔清醒，認真你便輸了&quot; 如果用你果句改左最後果句，我感覺好似失去左呢個味道。"}]}